[I] Ayatana Application Indicators Shared Library

[T] The Ayatana Indicators project is the continuation of Application
[T] Indicators and System Indicators, two technologies developed by Canonical
[T] Ltd. for the Unity7 desktop. Note: This library is Gtk and DBusMenu-based
[T] and considered obsolete. The libayatana-appindicator-glib should instead
[T] be used for new projects.

[U] https://github.com/AyatanaIndicators/libayatana-appindicator

[A] Ayatana developers
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/desktop/mate

[L] GPL
